title: Simple Solar Homesteading Ebook and Cabin Plans
description:
Simple Solar Homesteading Ebook
A great little ebook on how to build a cabin and take take of most of your needs

Contains Plans on a building a small cabin, solar water heaters,solar oven, solar 

power system with generator backup, a portable chicken coop, and more
